Subject: [PATCH RESEND v3 1/3] ptrace: pass type of a syscall-stop in
 ptrace_message
Message-ID: <20181125022227.55e8caf7@akathisia>
In-Reply-To: <20181125022150.46258a20@akathisia>
References: <20181125022150.46258a20@akathisia>
